claim.claim-text:
A denitration apparatus comprising:
a coal-fired boiler;
an economizer configured to be provided to the coal-fired boiler;
an upstream duct configured to guide exhaust gas from a upstream side of the economizer;
a downstream duct configured to guide exhaust gas from a downstream side of the economizer;
a first air preheater configured to be provided at a downstream side of the upstream duct;
a second air preheater configured to be provided at a downstream side of the downstream duct;
a denitration reactor configured to be provided at a upstream side of the first air preheater or the second air preheater;
a first bypass duct configured to be provided at a upstream side of the denitration reactor for connecting the upstream duct and the downstream duct; and
a second bypass duct configured to be provided at a downstream side of the denitration reactor for connecting the upstream duct and the downstream duct.
